                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc>
                            <supportDesc>
                                <support><p>Large irregular but broadly rectangular block of grey limestone (of moderate quality, not seemingly the compact Taormina limestone), damaged on all sides, especially upper and lower right. It is unclear whether either the top or the bottom of the text is preserved, but a clear vacat is visible at the end of lines 2, 3, and 4, although the stone is not intact on the right..</p>
